snippet.title: Starblind - Teaser
snippet.description:
If you like endless runners, you’ll love this game! It’s an epic adventure, set in a beautiful unexplored universe with stunning graphics and awesome music! Navigate through different obstacles such as meteors, spaceships and difficult terrain as you explore the beautiful sceneries space has to offer! So board the spaceship, meet the crew and explore every nook and cranny to find the best photos in the universe!
-----------
Ako voliš endless runner-e, obožavaćeš ovu igricu! Nesvakidašnja avantura, smještena u neistraženom univerzumu sa očaravajućom grafikom i upečatljivom muzikom! Savladaćeš razne prepreke, meteore i svemirske brodove u svojim ekspedicijama i otkriti ljepote koje nudi beskrajni svemir! Ukrcaj se u svoj svemirski brod, upoznaj ekipu i istraži svaku planetu u potrazi za najboljim fotkama u galaksiji!
